var data={"title":"Buprenorphine: Patient drug information","body":"<div id=\"topicContent\" class=\"utdArticleSection utdStyle\"><div id=\"disclaimer\">The content on the UpToDate website is not intended nor recommended as a substitute for medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.  Always seek the advice of your own physician or other qualified health care professional regarding any medical questions or conditions.\nThe use of UpToDate content is governed by the <a href=\"https://www.uptodate.com/legal/terms-of-use\" class=\"legal legal_termsofuse\">UpToDate Terms of Use</a>. &copy;2018 UpToDate, Inc. All rights reserved.</div><div id=\"drugTitle\">Buprenorphine: Patient drug information</div><div id=\"lexiTitleImg\"></div><div class=\"clear\"></div><div id=\"lcoSearchClickUrl\"><a href=\"http://online.lexi.com/lco/action/api/find/globalid/5768?utd=1\" target=\"_blank\">Access Lexicomp Online here.</a></div><div id=\"drugCopy\">Copyright 1978-2018 Lexicomp, Inc. All rights reserved.</div><div id=\"topicText\"><p>(For additional information <a href=\"topic.htm?path=buprenorphine-drug-information\" class=\"drug drug_general\">see &quot;Buprenorphine: Drug information&quot;</a> and <a href=\"topic.htm?path=buprenorphine-pediatric-drug-information\" class=\"drug drug_pediatric\">see &quot;Buprenorphine: Pediatric drug information&quot;</a>)</p><div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"F143056\" class=\"list ubnlist drugH1Div drugBrandNames\"><span class=\"drugH1\">Brand Names: US</span>\n                  <ul>\n                     <li>Belbuca;</li>\n                     <li>Buprenex;</li>\n                     <li>Butrans;</li>\n                     <li>Probuphine Implant Kit;</li>\n                     <li>Sublocade</li></ul></div>\r\n<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"F143057\" class=\"list cbnlist drugH1Div drugBrandNames\"><span class=\"drugH1\">Brand Names: Canada</span>\n                  <ul>\n                     <li>Belbuca;</li>\n                     <li>Butrans</li></ul></div>\r\n<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"F10024861\" class=\"ord-stmt war-os drugH1Div\"><span class=\"drugH1\">Warning</span>\n                  <ul style=\"list-style-type:none;\" class=\"statements\">\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2705324</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">All products:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4627342</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">This drug may cause very bad and sometimes deadly breathing problems. Call your doctor right away if you have slow, shallow, or trouble breathing.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699678</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Keep all drugs in a safe place. Keep all drugs out of the reach of children and pets.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5647950</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">This drug has an opioid drug in it. The use of opioid drugs along with a benzodiazepine drug or other drugs that may make you drowsy or slow your actions has led to very bad side effects. Side effects that have happened include slowed or trouble breathing and deaths. Benzodiazepine drugs include drugs like alprazolam, diazepam, and lorazepam. Benzodiazepine drugs are used to treat many health problems like anxiety, trouble sleeping, or seizures. Talk with the doctor.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4814182</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Many drugs interact with this drug and can raise the chance of side effects like deadly breathing problems. Talk with your doctor and pharmacist to make sure it is safe to use this drug with all of your drugs.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2700304</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not take with alcohol or products that have alcohol. Unsafe and sometimes deadly effects may happen.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6304548</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Get medical help right away if you feel very sleepy, very dizzy, or if you pass out. Caregivers or others need to get medical help right away if the patient does not respond, does not answer or react like normal, or will not wake up.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4726410</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span>\n                           <span class=\"gender list\">\n                              <span>Female</span></span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Using this drug for a long time during pregnancy may lead to withdrawal in the newborn baby. This can be life-threatening. Talk with the doctor.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6044473</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">All oral products, short-acting injection, and patch:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2697693</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">This drug may be habit-forming with long-term use.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4726402</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">This drug is a strong pain drug that can put you at risk for addiction, abuse, and misuse. Misuse or abuse of this drug can lead to overdose and death. Talk with your doctor.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2700435</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">You will be watched closely to make sure you do not misuse, abuse, or become addicted to this drug.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4468505</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not take more than what your doctor told you to take. Taking more than you are told may raise your chance of very bad side effects.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4726411</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">The chance of very bad and sometimes deadly breathing problems may be greater when you first start this drug or anytime your dose is raised.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4627302</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Even one dose of this drug may be deadly if it is taken by someone else or by accident, especially in children. If this drug is taken by someone else or by accident, get medical help right away.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4236128</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">All oral products:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5932187</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Misuse or abuse of this drug by chewing, swallowing, injecting, or snorting it can lead to overdose and death.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2705500</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Patch:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5126124</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Misuse or abuse of this drug by placing it in the mouth or chewing, swallowing, injecting, or snorting it can lead to overdose and death.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6044469</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Implant:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6044470</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Very bad problems can happen when this drug is put in or taken out. These include the implant moving, sticking out of the skin, or coming out by itself. This may cause nerve or blood vessel injury in the arm. It could be deadly if the implant or pieces of it move into the blood vessels or your lungs. Call your doctor right away if the implant sticks out of the skin or comes out by itself. Call your doctor right away if you have numbness or weakness in your arm, chest pain, or shortness of breath.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6044472</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">It is common to have itching, pain, irritation, redness, swelling, scarring, bleeding, or bruising where the implant is put in or taken out. Call the doctor if you have bleeding, or if any of these effects happen often or get worse.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6303805</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Long-acting injection:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6582559</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">This drug is given into the fatty part of the skin only. If given other ways (into a vein or muscle), this can be deadly. If you have questions, talk with the doctor.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6582561</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Implant and long-acting injection:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4645324</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">You may only get this drug through a special program. Talk with your doctor.</span></li></ul></div>\r\n<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"F10024863\" class=\"ord-stmt yya-os drugH1Div\"><span class=\"drugH1\">What is this drug used for?</span>\n                  <ul style=\"list-style-type:none;\" class=\"statements\">\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6044474</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Implant, long-acting injection, and under the tongue (sublingual) tablet:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2691820</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">It is used to treat pain drug (opioid) addiction.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6582561</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Implant and long-acting injection:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6044475</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">This drug is only for use by people who have been taking pain drugs (opioids) and are used to their effects. Talk with the doctor.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6303806</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Short-acting injection:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2691611</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">It is used to ease pain.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5932188</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Cheek film and patch:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5121262</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">It is used to ease very bad pain.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5121263</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">It is only to be used when around-the-clock (continuous) care is needed for a long time. It is also only to be used when other pain drugs do not treat your pain well enough or you cannot take them.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6044473</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">All oral products, short-acting injection, and patch:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2692146</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">It may be given to you for other reasons. Talk with the doctor.</span></li></ul></div>\r\n<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"F10024862\" class=\"ord-stmt coi-os drugH1Div\"><span class=\"drugH1\">What do I need to tell my doctor BEFORE I take this drug?</span>\n                  <ul style=\"list-style-type:none;\" class=\"statements\">\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2701662</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If you have an allergy to buprenorphine or any other part of this drug.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2705171</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If you are allergic to any drugs like this one, any other drugs, foods, or other substances. Tell your doctor about the allergy and what signs you had, like rash; hives; itching; shortness of breath; wheezing; cough; swelling of face, lips, tongue, or throat; or any other signs.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4627362</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If you have any of these health problems: Lung or breathing problems like asthma, trouble breathing, or sleep apnea; high levels of carbon dioxide in the blood; or stomach or bowel block or narrowing.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2703781</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If you have liver disease.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4640863</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If you or a family member have a long QT on ECG.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5932190</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If you are taking any of these drugs: Butorphanol, nalbuphine, or pentazocine.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4667886</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If you are using another drug that has the same drug in it.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4650704</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If you are taking any of these drugs: Certain drugs to treat a heartbeat that is not normal like amiodarone, disopyramide, dofetilide, procainamide, quinidine, or sotalol.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4647906</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If you are taking any drugs that can cause a certain type of heartbeat that is not normal (prolonged QT interval). There are many drugs that can do this. Ask your doctor or pharmacist if you are not sure.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2703859</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If you have taken certain drugs used for low mood (depression) like isocarboxazid, phenelzine, or tranylcypromine or drugs used for Parkinson's disease like selegiline or rasagiline in the last 14 days. Taking this drug within 14 days of those drugs can cause very bad high blood pressure.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4232023</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If you are taking any of these drugs: Linezolid or methylene blue.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4194403</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">This is not a list of all drugs or health problems that interact with this drug.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4194405</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Tell your doctor and pharmacist about all of your drugs (prescription or OTC, natural products, vitamins) and health problems. You must check to make sure that it is safe for you to take this drug with all of your drugs and health problems. Do not start, stop, or change the dose of any drug without checking with your doctor.</span></li></ul></div>\r\n<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"F10024867\" class=\"ord-stmt yye-os drugH1Div\"><span class=\"drugH1\">What are some things I need to know or do while I take this drug?</span>\n                  <ul style=\"list-style-type:none;\" class=\"statements\">\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s2705324</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">All products:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s2697633</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Tell all of your health care providers that you take this drug. This includes your doctors, nurses, pharmacists, and dentists. </span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s2858939</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Avoid driving and doing other tasks or actions that call for you to be alert until you see how this drug affects you.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s4201327</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">To lower the chance of feeling dizzy or passing out, rise slowly if you have been sitting or lying down. Be careful going up and down stairs.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s2698463</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Have blood work checked as you have been told by the doctor. Talk with the doctor.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s4650846</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">This drug may cause withdrawal symptoms if you are dependent or addicted to narcotics. Talk with your doctor.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s4645516</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Very bad and sometimes deadly liver problems have happened with this drug. Call your doctor right away if you have signs of liver problems like dark urine, feeling tired, not hungry, upset stomach or stomach pain, light-colored stools, throwing up, or yellow skin or eyes.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s6000677</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Long-term use of an opioid drug like this drug may lead to lower sex hormone levels. This may lead to signs like change in sex ability in men, no menstrual period in women, lowered interest in sex, or fertility problems. Call your doctor if you have any of these signs.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s4726448</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">This drug may raise the chance of seizures in some people, including people who have had seizures in the past. Talk to your doctor to see if you have a greater chance of seizures while taking this drug.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s2697004</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If you are 65 or older, use this drug with care. You could have more side effects.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s4232496</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span>\n                           <span class=\"gender list\">\n                              <span>Female</span></span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">This drug may cause harm to the unborn baby if you take it while you are pregnant. If you are pregnant or you get pregnant while taking this drug, call your doctor right away.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s6304013</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span>\n                           <span class=\"gender list\">\n                              <span>Female</span></span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Tell your doctor if you are breast-feeding or plan to breast-feed. This drug passes into breast milk and may harm your baby.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s2705500</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Patch:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s2696692</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Avoid use of heat sources (such as sunlamps, tanning beds, heating pads, electric blankets, heat lamps, saunas, hot tubs, heated waterbeds). Avoid long, hot baths or sunbathing. Your temperature may rise and cause too much drug to pass into your body.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s4650843</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If the sticky side of the patch touches another person's skin, wash the area with water only, and get medical help right away.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s6044473</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">All oral products, short-acting injection, and patch:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s4562525</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not stop taking this drug all of a sudden without calling your doctor. You may have a greater risk of signs of withdrawal. If you need to stop this drug, you will want to slowly stop it as ordered by your doctor.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s4194399</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If you have been taking this drug for a long time or at high doses, it may not work as well and you may need higher doses to get the same effect. This is known as tolerance. Call your doctor if this drug stops working well. Do not take more than ordered.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s6582562</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">\n                              <b>All products other than short-acting injection:</b></span></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s4468886</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">This drug is not approved for use in children. Talk with the doctor.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s6044474</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Implant, long-acting injection, and under the tongue (sublingual) tablet:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s2698489</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Follow up with the doctor as you have been told.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s6582564</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Be sure you know how to treat pain while you take this drug. Do not take opioid pain drugs unless your doctor tells you to. Pain drugs may not work as well while you take this drug. Do not take more pain drugs to try to get them to work. If you have an emergency, tell your health care provider that you take this drug. If you have questions, talk with your doctor.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s6582561</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Implant and long-acting injection:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s6582565</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If you need to stop treatment with this drug, you will need to watch for signs of withdrawal. Tell your doctor if you have any bad effects. If you have questions, talk with your doctor.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s6044507</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If this drug comes out by itself, keep it away from children. Accidental exposure may cause death. If someone else, especially a child, is exposed to this drug by accident, get medical help right away.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s6044508</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not try to take this drug out by yourself. This could lead to infection and withdrawal. Talk with your doctor.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b259:s6044509</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Try not to touch the area where this drug is put in very often. Touching it often may raise the chance of infection.</span></li></ul></div>\r\n<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"F10024870\" class=\"ord-stmt yyh-os drugH1Div\"><span class=\"drugH1\">What are some side effects that I need to call my doctor about right away?</span>\n                  <ul style=\"list-style-type:none;\" class=\"statements\">\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4186185</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>WARNING/CAUTION:</b> Even though it may be rare, some people may have very bad and sometimes deadly side effects when taking a drug. Tell your doctor or get medical help right away if you have any of the following signs or symptoms that may be related to a very bad side effect:</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2705324</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">All products:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699066</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Signs of an allergic reaction, like rash; hives; itching; red, swollen, blistered, or peeling skin with or without fever; wheezing; tightness in the chest or throat; trouble breathing, swallowing, or talking; unusual hoarseness; or swelling of the mouth, face, lips, tongue, or throat.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698639</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Trouble breathing, slow breathing, or shallow breathing.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699023</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Very bad dizziness or passing out.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698651</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Too much sweat.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4270262</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Fast or slow heartbeat.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4186197</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">A heartbeat that does not feel normal.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699058</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Feeling confused.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699014</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Very hard stools (constipation).</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698658</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Feeling very tired or weak.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698068</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Feeling nervous and excitable.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698079</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Fever or chills.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698350</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Sore throat.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2697935</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Change in balance.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698236</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Mood changes.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699008</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Very bad belly pain.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698039</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Extra muscle action or slow movement.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698349</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Slurred speech.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698360</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Swelling in the arms or legs.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2697967</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Change in eyesight.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4192394</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">A burning, numbness, or tingling feeling that is not normal.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698642</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Trouble speaking.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698626</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Chest pain or pressure.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698012</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Trouble passing urine.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698118</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Hallucinations (seeing or hearing things that are not there).</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698247</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Muscle or joint pain.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4236126</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Memory problems or loss.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699003</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Seizures.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699031</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Very bad headache.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698329</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Shakiness.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5112629</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Feeling very sleepy.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5230622</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">A very bad and sometimes deadly health problem called serotonin syndrome may happen if you take this drug with drugs for depression, migraines, or certain other drugs. Call your doctor right away if you have agitation; change in balance; confusion; hallucinations; fever; fast or abnormal heartbeat; flushing; muscle twitching or stiffness; seizures; shivering or shaking; sweating a lot; very bad diarrhea, upset stomach, or throwing up; or very bad headache.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6000678</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Taking an opioid drug like this drug may lead to a rare but very bad adrenal gland problem. Call your doctor right away if you have very bad dizziness or passing out, very bad upset stomach or throwing up, or if you feel less hungry, very tired, or very weak.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6303806</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Short-acting injection:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698189</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Irritation where the shot is given.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2705500</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Patch:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699049</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Very bad skin irritation.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6044469</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Implant:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2697997</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Low mood (depression).</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6582561</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Implant and long-acting injection:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698187</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Irritation where this drug is given.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6044510</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Swelling, warmth, or redness where this drug was given.</span></li></ul></div>\r\n<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"F10024868\" class=\"ord-stmt yyf-os drugH1Div\"><span class=\"drugH1\">What are some other side effects of this drug?</span>\n                  <ul style=\"list-style-type:none;\" class=\"statements\">\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4186184</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">All drugs may cause side effects. However, many people have no side effects or only have minor side effects. Call your doctor or get medical help if any of these side effects or any other side effects bother you or do not go away:</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2705324</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">All products:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2697975</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Hard stools (constipation).</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698017</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Dizziness.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4192396</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Feeling sleepy.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698261</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Upset stomach or throwing up.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2697891</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Belly pain.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698074</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Feeling tired or weak.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698119</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Headache.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2705500</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Patch:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698344</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Skin irritation.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6044469</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Implant:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5152902</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Tooth pain.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2697883</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Back pain.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5550879</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Mouth pain.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4794762</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Throat pain.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698162</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Not able to sleep.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699671</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">These are not all of the side effects that may occur. If you have questions about side effects, call your doctor. Call your doctor for medical advice about side effects.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4577343</span>\n                           <span class=\"country-exclude list\">\n                              <span>US</span></span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">You may report side effects to your national health agency.</span></li></ul></div>\r\n<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"F10024865\" class=\"ord-stmt yyc-os drugH1Div\"><span class=\"drugH1\">How is this drug best taken?</span>\n                  <ul style=\"list-style-type:none;\" class=\"statements\">\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2696083</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Use this drug as ordered by your doctor. Read all information given to you. Follow all instructions closely.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2705324</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">All products:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s3927405</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not take this drug with other strong pain drugs or if you are using a pain patch without talking to your doctor first.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4128402</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If you drink grapefruit juice or eat grapefruit often, talk with your doctor.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2893560</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Under the tongue (sublingual) tablet:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4471686</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Place tablet under the tongue and let melt.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4726056</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not chew or swallow whole.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4650943</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not eat, drink, smoke, or talk while this drug is melting.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5932188</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Cheek film and patch:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5007782</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not use if the pouch that holds this drug is torn, open, or not sealed all the way.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2694786</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not use for fast pain relief or on an as needed basis.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4627413</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not use for pain relief after surgery if you have not been taking drugs like this drug.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2696397</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Cheek film:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5932200</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not use this drug if it is cut, damaged, or changed in any way.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5932201</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not put this drug on any areas with sores.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699642</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Use right after opening.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2696258</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Wash your hands before use.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4497282</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Be sure your hands are dry before you touch this drug.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2696392</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Wet the inside of your cheek with your tongue or water.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5932202</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Place the film inside the mouth on a wet cheek. Place the yellow side of the film against the inside of the cheek. Hold for 5 seconds so it sticks to the cheek. Let it melt.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5932203</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not touch or move this drug with your tongue or finger after it has been placed.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s3370403</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not eat or drink until this drug has melted all the way.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2705500</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Patch:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2694797</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not use patches that are cut or do not look right.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2696257</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Wash your hands before and after use.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2695570</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Take off old patch first.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2989499</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Put patch on clean, dry, healthy skin on the upper arm, upper back, upper chest, or side of the chest.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2694628</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Clip hair at site before putting patch on. Do not shave.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2695471</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Put the patch in a new area each time you change the patch.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4650966</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not put a new patch on the same skin area as an old patch for at least 21 days.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2695146</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If the patch falls off, put a new one on.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s3688608</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If the patch loosens, put tape ONLY on the edges of the patch to hold it in place.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5756870</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If there are problems with the patch not sticking, cover the patch with dressings as you have been told.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s5756877</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not put on more than 1 patch at the same time unless your doctor tells you to.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2705493</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">All oral products and skin patch:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2696130</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">To gain the most benefit, do not miss doses.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2695852</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Take this drug at the same time of day.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6303806</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Short-acting injection:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2695976</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">It is given as a shot into a muscle or vein.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6303805</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Long-acting injection:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2696001</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">It is given as a shot into the fatty part of the skin.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2696366</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Your doctor will give this drug.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2694681</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not use pressure (waist band or belt) on the part where the shot is given.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6044469</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Implant:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6044511</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">It is put in as an implant under the skin.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6044512</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If the implant is sticking out of the skin or comes out by itself, call your doctor right away. Follow what your doctor has told you to do.</span></li></ul></div>\r\n<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"F10024866\" class=\"ord-stmt yyd-os drugH1Div\"><span class=\"drugH1\">What do I do if I miss a dose?</span>\n                  <ul style=\"list-style-type:none;\" class=\"statements\">\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4236128</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">All oral products:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2696563</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Take a missed dose as soon as you think about it.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2696496</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If it is close to the time for your next dose, skip the missed dose and go back to your normal time.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2696475</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not take 2 doses at the same time or extra doses.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2705500</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Patch:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2696442</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Put on a missed patch as soon as you think about it after taking off the old one.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2696453</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not apply double dose or extra doses.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6044514</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Implant and all injection products:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2696446</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Call your doctor to find out what to do.</span></li></ul></div>\r\n<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"F10024871\" class=\"ord-stmt yyi-os drugH1Div\"><span class=\"drugH1\">How do I store and/or throw out this drug?</span>\n                  <ul style=\"list-style-type:none;\" class=\"statements\">\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2705493</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">All oral products and skin patch:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699336</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Store at room temperature.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699266</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Store in a dry place. Do not store in a bathroom.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2696397</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Cheek film:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699403</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Store in foil pouch until ready for use.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2705500</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Patch:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699524</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Store patches in pouch until ready for use.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699145</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">After you take off a skin patch, be sure to fold the sticky sides of the patch to each other.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4790826</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Follow the info that comes with this drug for throwing out patches that are used or not needed. Check with your pharmacist if you have questions about how to throw out this drug. </span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s6044514</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Implant and all injection products:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699596</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If you need to store this drug at home, talk with your doctor, nurse, or pharmacist about how to store it.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2705324</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">\n                           <b>\n                              <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">All products:</span></b></span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s4194563</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Throw away unused or expired drugs. Do not flush down a toilet or pour down a drain unless you are told to do so. Check with your pharmacist if you have questions about the best way to throw out drugs. There may be drug take-back programs in your area.</span></li></ul></div>\r\n<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"F10024872\" class=\"ord-stmt yyj-os drugH1Div\"><span class=\"drugH1\">General drug facts</span>\n                  <ul style=\"list-style-type:none;\" class=\"statements\">\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699675</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If your symptoms or health problems do not get better or if they become worse, call your doctor. </span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699673</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Do not share your drugs with others and do not take anyone else's drugs.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699677</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Keep a list of all your drugs (prescription, natural products, vitamins, OTC) with you. Give this list to your doctor.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699683</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Talk with the doctor before starting any new drug, including prescription or OTC, natural products, or vitamins.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2699709</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span>\n                           <span class=\"country-exclude list\">\n                              <span>US</span></span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">Some drugs may have another patient information leaflet. If you have any questions about this drug, please talk with your doctor, nurse, pharmacist, or other health care provider.</span></li>\n                     <li class=\"statement\">\n                        <span style=\"display:none;\" class=\"attributes\">\n                           <span class=\"link\">urn:lims:b498:s2698721</span>\n                           <span class=\"entity\">&bull;</span></span>\n                        <span class=\"content\">If you think there has been an overdose, call your poison control center or get medical care right away. Be ready to tell or show what was taken, how much, and when it happened.</span></li></ul></div>\r\n</div><div id=\"topicAgreement\">Use of UpToDate is subject to the <a href=\"https://www.uptodate.com/legal/license\" class=\"licenseLink\" id=\"sla_in_page\">Subscription and License Agreement</a>.</div><div id=\"topicVersionRevision\">Topic 11493 Version 156.0</div></div>","outline":"<div id=\"outlineSections\"><h2>Topic Outline</h2><ul><li class=\"plainItem\"><a sectionName=\"Brand Names: US\" href=\"#F143056\" class=\"outlineLink\">Brand Names: US</a></li><li class=\"plainItem\"><a sectionName=\"Brand Names: Canada\" href=\"#F143057\" class=\"outlineLink\">Brand Names: Canada</a></li><li class=\"plainItem\"><a sectionName=\"Warning\" href=\"#F10024861\" class=\"outlineLink\">Warning</a></li><li class=\"plainItem\"><a sectionName=\"What is this drug used for?\" href=\"#F10024863\" class=\"outlineLink\">What is this drug used for?</a></li><li class=\"plainItem\"><a sectionName=\"What do I need to tell my doctor BEFORE I take this drug?\" href=\"#F10024862\" class=\"outlineLink\">What do I need to tell my doctor BEFORE I take this drug?</a></li><li class=\"plainItem\"><a sectionName=\"What are some things I need to know or do while I take this drug?\" href=\"#F10024867\" class=\"outlineLink\">What are some things I need to know or do while I take this drug?</a></li><li class=\"plainItem\"><a sectionName=\"What are some side effects that I need to call my doctor about right away?\" href=\"#F10024870\" class=\"outlineLink\">What are some side effects that I need to call my doctor about right away?</a></li><li class=\"plainItem\"><a sectionName=\"What are some other side effects of this drug?\" href=\"#F10024868\" class=\"outlineLink\">What are some other side effects of this drug?</a></li><li class=\"plainItem\"><a sectionName=\"How is this drug best taken?\" href=\"#F10024865\" class=\"outlineLink\">How is this drug best taken?</a></li><li class=\"plainItem\"><a sectionName=\"What do I do if I miss a dose?\" href=\"#F10024866\" class=\"outlineLink\">What do I do if I miss a dose?</a></li><li class=\"plainItem\"><a sectionName=\"How do I store and/or throw out this drug?\" href=\"#F10024871\" class=\"outlineLink\">How do I store and/or throw out this drug?</a></li><li class=\"plainItem\"><a sectionName=\"General drug facts\" href=\"#F10024872\" class=\"outlineLink\">General drug facts</a></li></ul></div><div><h2>RELATED TOPICS</h2><div id=\"outlineTopics\"><ul><li><a href=\"topic.htm?path=buprenorphine-drug-information\" class=\"drug drug_general\">Buprenorphine: Drug information</a></li><li><a href=\"topic.htm?path=buprenorphine-pediatric-drug-information\" class=\"drug drug_pediatric\">Buprenorphine: Pediatric drug information</a></li></ul></div></div>","javascript":null}